title: EARLY DOORS SERIES 1
description:
Starring: Craig Cash, Rodney Litchfield, Rita May, Christine Bottomley, John Henshaw, Phil Mealey.

Directed by: Adrian Shergold

A gentle yet compelling story of life, love, loneliness and blocked urinals. Each evening, the regulars bring their particular foibles and characterstics up to the bar. Overhearing their conversations and reliving the events in each of their lives is both moving and amusing.
